text:
Horace Harding Boulevard, east from about 228th Street, toward Alley Pond. This is the former West Alley Road which was later widened and made Horace Harding Boulevard.

P. L. Sperr
June 6, 1927
Views 1,2
title: Queens: Horace Harding Boule - 228th Street
